<LI>Function menu.</LI>
<LI>Automatic '{...}' blocks.</LI>
<LI>Shortcuts for increasing and decreasing the indent.</LI>
<LI>Source file splitting to find error positions.</LI>
<LI>Complete error tracking and deletion.</LI>
</UL>
